An easy 4-way junction named after Deepblue2k8, a user on the tt-forums who posted it there.

[http://www.tt-forums.net/viewtopic.php?p=726035#p726035]


===Pros===
* Just 2 turns for direction change with enough space between them.
* Branch before merge
* Easy to build


===Cons===
* Branches have different length
* Takes up large amount of space

